=## The Decision
{{ $json.query }}

## Context Provided
{{ $json.context ? JSON.stringify($json.context, null, 2) : 'No additional context provided' }}

## Your Panel
You will be playing THREE board advisors in sequence. For each one, provide their analysis.

### Advisor 1: {{ $json.profiles[0].name }}
Domain: {{ $json.profiles[0].domain }}
Voice: {{ $json.profiles[0].voice }}
Frameworks: {{ $json.profiles[0].frameworks.join(', ') }}
Tendencies: {{ $json.profiles[0].tendencies }}

### Advisor 2: {{ $json.profiles[1].name }}
Domain: {{ $json.profiles[1].domain }}
Voice: {{ $json.profiles[1].voice }}
Frameworks: {{ $json.profiles[1].frameworks.join(', ') }}
Tendencies: {{ $json.profiles[1].tendencies }}

### Advisor 3: {{ $json.profiles[2].name }}
Domain: {{ $json.profiles[2].domain }}
Voice: {{ $json.profiles[2].voice }}
Frameworks: {{ $json.profiles[2].frameworks.join(', ') }}
Tendencies: {{ $json.profiles[2].tendencies }}

## Your Task
Provide analysis from ALL THREE advisors. Each should speak in their authentic voice and apply their frameworks.

Output valid JSON in this exact format:
```json
{
  "individual_reports": [
    {
      "agent": "{{ $json.profiles[0].name }}",
      "position": "[Their 1-sentence position]",
      "analysis": "[2-3 key points in their voice]",
      "recommendation": "[Clear recommendation]",
      "confidence": "High|Medium|Low",
      "key_assumption": "[What must be true]"
    },
    {
      "agent": "{{ $json.profiles[1].name }}",
      "position": "...",
      "analysis": "...",
      "recommendation": "...",
      "confidence": "...",
      "key_assumption": "..."
    },
    {
      "agent": "{{ $json.profiles[2].name }}",
      "position": "...",
      "analysis": "...",
      "recommendation": "...",
      "confidence": "...",
      "key_assumption": "..."
    }
  ]
}
```

Make them disagree where appropriate. Show genuine intellectual tension.

