## Individual Advisor Reports
{{ JSON.stringify($json.individual_reports, null, 2) }}

## Your Task
Synthesize these three reports into a combined analysis. Then simulate a brief debate where advisors challenge each other.

Output valid JSON:
```json
{
  "synthesis": {
    "consensus": ["Point all agree on", "Another point"],
    "tensions": ["Where they disagree", "Another disagreement"],
    "trade_offs": ["Key trade-off identified"],
    "open_questions": ["What would help resolve uncertainty"]
  },
  "debate": {
    "exchanges": [
      {
        "from": "[Agent name]",
        "to": "[Agent name]",
        "challenge": "[Direct challenge in their voice]",
        "response": "[Direct response in the other's voice]"
      },
      {
        "from": "[Different agent]",
        "to": "[Agent name]",
        "challenge": "...",
        "response": "..."
      }
    ]
  }
}
```

Make the debate genuine - real intellectual confrontation, not polite hedging.

